create 2d character array xx with size 8 by 30
create integer n
while read n is true
create character array yy with size 30 with yy = " + - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - + "
copy string from yy to xx [ 0 ]
create character array zz with size 30 with zz = " | # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . | D | ) "
copy string from zz to xx [ 1 ]
create character array k with size 30 with k = " | # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . | . | "
copy string from k to xx [ 2 ]
create character array kk with size 30 with kk = " | # . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . | "
copy string from kk to xx [ 3 ]
create character array ss with size 30 with ss = " | # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . # . | . | ) "
copy string from ss to xx [ 4 ]
create character array tt with size 30 with tt = " + - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - + "
copy string from tt to xx [ 5 ]
create integer a with a = 0
for i = 0 to 30 exclusive
for j = 0 to 6 exclusive
if xx [ j ] [ i ] is " # "
set xx [ j ] [ i ] to ' O '
increment a

if a is n , break loop
